title: Stroke Support Group
description: This support group is open to all. Topics rotate w/focus on life after stroke, education & prevention. Held every Thursday at 10:30 am.

title: Parkinson’s Support Group – CDA
description: CdA Parkinson’s Support Group meets the first Thursday of every month.  Sessions are open to those with Parkinson’s, their spouses, family & caregivers. This is a group of people who get together to support each other in our quest to live life to the fullest, in spite of the fact that we have Parkinson’s.
